### Services Layer (New)

#### [NEW] [eventTracker.js](file:///c:/Users/teste/Desktop/Singularidade/src/services/eventTracker.js)
Central event tracking service. Stores events in `localStorage` table `sg_events`. Every event records `eventName`, `timestamp`, `sessionId`, `payload`. Functions: `trackEvent(name, payload)`, `getEvents()`, `getEventsByType(name)`.

#### [NEW] [sessionManager.js](file:///c:/Users/teste/Desktop/Singularidade/src/services/sessionManager.js)
Session management. Generates `sessionId` (UUID v4) on first access, stores in `sessionStorage`. Captures UTM params and referrer from URL. Functions: `getSession()`, `getSessionId()`.

#### [NEW] [leadService.js](file:///c:/Users/teste/Desktop/Singularidade/src/services/leadService.js)
